OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOccasional showers heavy and
OL,6,Fwintry at times. Some bright spells
OL,7,Fand sunny intervals developing between
OL,8,Fshowers at times especially in the
OL,9,Feast. A cold day, with fresh to strong
OL,10,Fwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few showers this evening,
OL,13,Fstill wintry on high ground, then
OL,14,Fbecoming dry overnight with clear
OL,15,Fspells. Winds easing and allowing a
OL,16,Ftouch of frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FMostly dry on Monday, some
OL,19,Fsunshine but clouding over, patchy
OL,20,Frain for Isles where southerly winds
OL,21,Fwill strengthen later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
