OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSunny
OL,6,Fstart Tuesday, warm in east, then rain
OL,7,Freaching west later, some heavy.
OL,8,FOccasional rain or showers on
OL,9,FWednesday. Sunny intervals and showers
OL,10,Fon Thursday.
